RESEARCH ARTICLE
Heat shock-induced chaperoning by Hsp70 is enabled in-cell

Drishti Guin1, Hannah Gelman2¤, Yuhan WangID3, Martin GruebeleID1,2,3*
1 Department of Chemistry, University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign, Urbana, Illinois, United States of America, 2 Department of Physics, University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign, Urbana, Illinois, United States of America, 3 Center for Biophysics and Quantitative Biology, University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign, Urbana, Illinois, United States of America

