which we refer to as Hsp70 throughout. To study binding, we engineered a FRET pair consisting of mHsp70 (Hsp70 labeled by the red acceptor mCherry at the C-terminus) and ePGK (PGK labeled by the green donor mEGFP at the N-terminus) (Fig 1B). mCherry and mEGFP

